Ip address:
Ip address numbers should be in 0 to 255 number only like 0-255.0-255.0-255.0-255

Representation of IP address in ipv4 format:

0-255   . 0-255  .0-255   . 0-255
--------|--------|--------|--------
4 bytes |4 bytes |4 bytes |4 bytes
8 bit   | 8bit   |8bit    |8bit

